{"title" : "夏、冬令营" , "leftimage":["xdly1.jpg","xdly2.jpg","xdly3.jpg"],"content":"<P class=MsoNormal style='LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none'><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312'>金牌拓展每年暑期与寒假，定期在军营举办</SPAN><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312'>9-16<SPAN lang=ZH-CN>岁青少年“自强、自立、感恩素质培养”主题式夏、冬令营活动。</SPAN><?xml:namespace prefix = 'o' ns = 'urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office' /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none'><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312'><SPAN style='mso-spacerun: yes'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style='mso-spacerun: yes'>&nbsp;</SPAN><SPAN lang=ZH-CN>“自强、自立、感恩素质培养”主题夏、冬令营的课程安排，特聘有</SPAN>20<SPAN lang=ZH-CN>余年</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体'>幼教从业经验的专业人士进行指导编排，在国内传统幼儿教育的基础上，</SPAN><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312'>借鉴国外蒙梭利教育体系，以孩子们自发的参与和动手能力为主，讲解为辅。秉承“每个孩子都是未来闪亮之星”的激励原则，发掘孩子的优点，让孩子在快乐中强化自己的优势。</SPAN><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none'><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312'><SPAN style='mso-spacerun: yes'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style='mso-spacerun: yes'>&nbsp;</SPAN><SPAN lang=ZH-CN>金牌青少年“自强、自立、感恩素质培养”主题式夏、冬令营，培训地点选择在军营，日常生活作息管理采用半军事化管理，半军事化管理是考虑孩子们的年龄与性格特点，将教育与实际充分相结合，以达成孩子们对自我与团队的认知、对良好的生活学习习惯成效的认知、给予与获得辩证关系的认知。</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none'><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312'><SPAN style='mso-spacerun: yes'>&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style='mso-spacerun: yes'>&nbsp;</SPAN><SPAN style='mso-spacerun: yes'>&nbsp;</SPAN><SPAN lang=ZH-CN>“自强、自立、感恩素质培养”主题，是青少年成长过程中的必修课程，将有效的帮助青少年面对人生中可能遇到的压力、沟通障碍、胆怯与独立性，塑造孩子的意志品质、与人沟通能力、自我管理能力、抗挫折能力、感恩的情怀！</SPAN><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none'><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none'><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312'><SPAN style='mso-spacerun: yes'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN lang=ZH-CN>报名参加办法：</SPAN><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: 30pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.5; mso-layout-grid-align: none'><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312'>学校等青少年团体与</SPAN><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312'>6-16<SPAN lang=ZH-CN>岁个人均可报名，满</SPAN>10<SPAN lang=ZH-CN>人成班，详见当期网站活动通知。</SPAN><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>"}